            "title": "Pfizer to Sell BioNTech Stake, Sources Tell Bloomberg",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><p>\n  By Nicholas G. Miller </p><br/><p>\n  --Pfizer is trying to sell its stake in BioNTech SE, Bloomberg reported, citing people familiar with the matter. </p><!-- Article --><p>\n\n  --Pfizer is offering 4.55 million American depositary receipts for $108 to $111.70 a share, according to the report. </p><br/><p>\n  The full article: <span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTJnlyO=p0Ny2A9w2jO=O6La9iIahZIahaKx2nEzBjN=kMKwpIO=lfK=lbAw2LIxQf5vpiIvkqIx20Jn2jIvkaIyB09mpAJngPLml8owBjN=k8EwpRonkbD\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'dow_jones', '51666408');\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-11-13/pfizer-looks-to-sell-stake-in-pandemic-vaccine-partner-biontech</span></p><br/><p>\n\n  Write to Nicholas G. Miller at nicholas.miller@wsj.com. </p><br/><p>\n  (END) Dow Jones Newswires</p><p>\n\n  11-13-25 0645ET</p></div>",
